original_title: Rise in Dengue Cases Reported from Nine Districts
original_body_lines: COLOMBO (News 1st) - The National Dengue Control Unit has announced that the number of dengue patients reported from nine districts has increased.Community Medical Specialist Dr. Prashila Samaraweera of the National Dengue Control Unit says that a total of 38,764 dengue patients have been reported from across the country during the recent period.
